    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The simple span processor passes finished recordables to the configured <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1trace_1_1SpanExporter" kindref="compound">SpanExporter</ref>, as soon as they are finished.</para>
<para>OnEnd and ForceFlush are no-ops.</para>
<para>All calls to the configured <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1trace_1_1SpanExporter" kindref="compound">SpanExporter</ref> are synchronized using a spin-lock on an atomic_flag. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
